name: Habazz The Avarice
description:
"..the sea of miners and slaves eventually breached into the vault and inside it, Habazz was already waiting with a poisoned wine on his hand. then without any wavering, he gave his last boast:

'greed is a bottomless pit, and i am the viper king that nestles within..'

Thus, was the end of Habazz The Avarice and soon after him, The Gold Trade of Malamun."

-Umayad, Sadalin. "History of The Malamun's Gold Rush"
